Package arcade.core.util

Class Graph.Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.core.util.Graph.Edge
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PatchComponentSitesGraph.SiteEdge
    Enclosing class:
    Graph
    public static class Graph.Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    Nested class representing a graph edge.

    The edge tracks its corresponding nodes as well as the edges into the FROM node and out of the TO node.
